  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of a continuous hepatic
      arterial infusion combination therapy with OPC-18 and 5-FU versus BST in patients with highly
      advanced hepatocellular carcinoma for which resection therapy or local therapy is
      inapplicable due to advanced vascular invasion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
